In 3'S  
  
  *This amazing example of the beauty of conflict/resolution in music*  
  *is found on the LPs "Check Your Head" and "The In Sounds From Way*  
  *Out"-instrumental.*  
  
  *Main progression*  
  *Guitar must be up and down strumming and make it funky!*  
  [-8-8--9--8-8----8-8--11-11--  
  -8-8--9--8-8----8-8--10-10--  
  ----------------------------  
  ----------------------------  
  ----------------------------  
  ----------------------------]  
  
  *Bridge*  
  *Then this part comes in after the Bass slows the song down!*  
  [----------------------------  
  --------4---------4---------  
  -3--5-5----3-3--5-------end on the --3--5--  
  ----------------------------  
  ----------------------------  
  ----------------------------]  
  *that's as good as it gets without a Moog!*<!--n:In 3'S:s:0:e:1040-->
